'''''I Told You So''''' ni firime yo muri Gana yo mu 1970<ref>I TOLD YOU SO (1970): A GHANAIAN FILM NOIR - Ghana ... <nowiki>https://www.ghanafilmindustry.com</nowiki> › i-told-you-so-gha...</ref>. Filime yerekana abanya [[Gana]] nuburyo bwabo bwo kubaho muburyo bwo gusebanya<ref>I TOLD YOU SO- first Ever Ghanaian movie, lady in 80's <nowiki>https://tugamedia.com</nowiki> › i-told-you-so-first-ever-ghanai...</ref> <ref>I Told You So (film) - Hyperleap <nowiki>https://hyperleap.com</nowiki> › topic › I_Told_You_So_(film)</ref>. Iratanga kandi ubushishozi mubuzima bw'umukobwa ukiri muto utakiriye inama za se mugihe agiye kurongora umugabo<ref>I told You So to play at Conference Centre - Graphic Online <nowiki>https://www.graphic.com.gh</nowiki> › Showbiz › Showbiz News</ref>, ntacyo yari azi kumugabo agiye kurongora, ahubwo yakiriye inama za nyina na nyirarume kuko agendera k'ubutunzi n'imbaraga umugabo afite<ref>'I TOLD YOU SO' A 1970 Ghanaian Movie - Enfexgh <nowiki>https://www.enfexgh.com</nowiki> › i-told-you-so-a-1970-ghanaia...</ref>.

Uyu mukobwa ukiri muto yaje kumenya ko umugabo agomba kurongora yari igisambo cyitwaje imbunda<ref>Classic Ghanaian Film: I Told You So - Ghana Rising <nowiki>http://ghanarising.blogspot.com</nowiki> › 2013/06 › classic-gha...</ref> . Ntiyishimiye ibyabaye byose. Papa abajije uko byagenze, asubiza ko umugabo yagombaga kurongora ari umujura witwaje imbunda; ise yarangije avuga ati "Nakubwiye gutya"<ref>...I Told You So | New Day Films <nowiki>https://www.newday.com</nowiki> › film › i-told-you-so</ref>.   

